{"tid":561121,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】外置硬碟過唔到嘢","createTime":"2018-02-14T17:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T02:40:35.000Z","uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c04279d3abf2185afd0ebfe55cd129b139a92633","tid":561121,"uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/014325_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F014325_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=00b831c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係macbook用家，之前將個harddisk(如圖) 插左落window, 無禁退出就忟左隻harddisk出黎，自此之後，佢就load十世先load到啲檔案出黎，但會好lag。<br />\n<br />\n然後我買左個新嘅harddisk打算backup返舊呢隻啲檔案<br />\ncopy落去個時佢show個畫面寫住：正在準備拷貝到｢xxx硬碟｣<br />\n卡左係呢個畫面兩日，load左兩日都係正在準備。<br />\n小弟對呢方面真係0知識，巴打們可否打救下我<br />\n啲檔案好重要。我要點先過到啲檔案落去 定等多幾日，由佢慢慢load。"},{"pid":"740aa3724ce7cf2d28e1de4c75c0548fff9ae95f","tid":561121,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"手動搵返邊d file爛左，之後用修復軟件嘗試修復，你咁過，一世都過唔到"},{"pid":"7123b527a7f566d43b3869a6fcbd513d49f63fc4","tid":561121,"uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740aa3724ce7cf2d28e1de4c75c0548fff9ae95f","tid":561121,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"手動搵返邊d file爛左，之後用修復軟件嘗試修復，你咁過，一世都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"修復過 佢話修復完成"},{"pid":"83c51cc082b2ff20e61f5b0f32613afec7eb8eb5","tid":561121,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7123b527a7f566d43b3869a6fcbd513d49f63fc4","tid":561121,"uid":167095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740aa3724ce7cf2d28e1de4c75c0548fff9ae95f","tid":561121,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"手動搵返邊d file爛左，之後用修復軟件嘗試修復，你咁過，一世都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201